00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:13,780
exposed Chu Qiao

287
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:15,260
in front of everyone.

288
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:17,950
It means Yan Xun lost an assistant.

289
00:14:19,170 --> 00:14:21,180
Doesn’t he fear Yan Xun will hate him?

290
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:25,440
He must have a backup plan, I guess.

291
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:27,780
Tell our men

292
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,650
to wait

293
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:31,220
for my order.

294
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:33,820
You’re going to...

295
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:36,870
Since he is here,

296
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:38,440
I’ll take some action against him.

297
00:14:39,210 --> 00:14:40,520
If we manage

298
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,870
to get rid of Xiao Ce this time,

299
00:14:42,810 --> 00:14:44,020
my brother will have the chance

300
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:45,510
to be the Crown Prince.

301
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:48,690
That would be perfect.

302
00:14:59,300 --> 00:15:00,390
Your Majesty,

303
00:15:00,730 --> 00:15:02,910
who is Chu Qiao

304
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:04,640
that came yesterday?

305
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:08,320
She is Yan Xun’s maid.

306
00:15:08,450 --> 00:15:09,720
In early years,

307
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:12,150
she worked for the Yuwen family.

308
00:15:13,660 --> 00:15:16,860
You stood up for her yesterday.

309
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,870
What?

310
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:20,220
You’re interested in her?

311
00:15:23,180 --> 00:15:25,610
I just find her amazing

312
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:27,540
when she works in the army

313
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:28,680
as a girl.

314
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:30,840
Besides, the Crown Prince of Liang

315
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:33,490
looks like a real playboy.

316
00:15:33,670 --> 00:15:34,840
I’m sure

317
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,190
he doesn’t like Chu Qiao with true heart.

318
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:38,180
I think

319
00:15:38,450 --> 00:15:40,110
he asked for trouble deliberately.

320
00:15:40,710 --> 00:15:42,250
Whatever.

321
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,760
Chu Qiao is

322
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,130
a useful girl.

323
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:47,740
Unfortunately,

324
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:50,870
she is only loyal to Yan Xun.

325
00:15:51,410 --> 00:15:54,740
Otherwise, I could make her

326
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:56,360
your personal guard

327
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:58,870
for the sake that you helped her.

328
00:16:00,010 --> 00:16:02,640
I don’t need anyone else to protect me.

329
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:03,680
Your Majesty,

330
00:16:04,370 --> 00:16:06,810
all I need is your love.

331
00:16:20,890 --> 00:16:21,890
By the way,

332
00:16:22,010 --> 00:16:24,040
have you decided

333
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,960
who to marry the Crown Prince of Liang?

334
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:32,150
Only my daughter Yuan Chun

335
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:34,830
is of the right age.

336
00:16:37,190 --> 00:16:38,810
But the Crown Prince of Liang

337
00:16:38,810 --> 00:16:40,200
looks so frivolous.

338
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,680
Do you really want Princess Chun

339
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:42,900
to marry him?

340
00:16:44,130 --> 00:16:45,440
The Emperor of Liang

341
00:16:46,170 --> 00:16:47,680
only has two sons.

342
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:51,390
The other one has a humble mother

343
00:16:51,390 --> 00:16:52,750
and he’s weak.

344
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,340
Therefore,

345
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:57,640
Xiao Ce is his father’s treasure.

346
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:00,360
Becoming the Crown Prince
at the age of six

347
00:17:00,690 --> 00:17:02,120
makes him a noble man.

348
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:05,430
He is a playboy,

349
00:17:05,710 --> 00:17:07,560
but that’s not big problem.

350
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:09,840
After marrying him,

351
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:11,510
Chun will be his legal wife.

352
00:17:12,250 --> 00:17:14,930
When Xiao Ce becomes the Emperor,

353
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:16,870
she will be the Empress.

354
00:17:17,620 --> 00:17:19,900
It brings no disgrace to her.

355
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:23,560
You’re right, Your Majesty.

356
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,090
Your Highness.

357
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:35,300
His Majesty told Concubine Lan

358
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:36,330
he would marry you

359
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:37,990
to the Crown Prince of Liang.

360
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:39,530
What?

361
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,240
Are you sure?

362
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,220
Yes.

363
00:17:42,650 --> 00:17:43,840
Father will marry me

364
00:17:43,980 --> 00:17:45,540
to Xiao Ce,

365
00:17:45,780 --> 00:17:47,520
the playboy?

366
00:17:48,090 --> 00:17:49,840
Yes.

367
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:00,940
Your Majesty,

368
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:02,840
the three-year period is almost due.

369
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:05,790
As you promised,

370
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:08,370
Yan Xun can go back to Yanbei.

371
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:09,780
In the past two years,

372
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:12,040
Yan Xun has been very careful

373
00:18:12,040 --> 00:18:13,180
and respectful.

374
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,670
However, Your Majesty,

375
00:18:14,990 --> 00:18:16,720
he is still a threat.

376
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,620
The more carefully he acts,

377
00:18:17,620 --> 00:18:19,310
the more ambitious he is.

378
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:21,870
If we let him go,

379
00:18:21,870 --> 00:18:23,920
there’ll be great trouble.

380
00:18:24,290 --> 00:18:26,590
He is Yan Shicheng’s son, anyway.

381
00:18:29,050 --> 00:18:32,330
I have spared him.

382
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:35,460
My people keep an eye on me.

383
00:18:35,460 --> 00:18:38,010
Also, the Crown Prince of Liang has come.

384
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,240
Are you asking me

385
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:42,490
to go back on my words?

386
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:45,290
We can kill him in many ways,

387
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,970
for example, assassination or poisoning.

388
00:18:47,270 --> 00:18:48,190
Anyway,

389
00:18:48,360 --> 00:18:51,110
we mustn’t let him leave Chang’an, alive.

390
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:53,900
You and Wei Guang

391
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,820
tried many times.

392
00:18:55,820 --> 00:18:56,830
Have you ever succeeded?

393
00:18:56,830 --> 00:18:59,180
I am trying to help you, Your Majesty.

394
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:04,120
The problem is

395
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,260
even if he dies in an accident,

396
00:19:05,260 --> 00:19:06,280
people will assume

397
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:08,000
I have him killed.

398
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:10,400
We must care for people’s gossip.

399
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:12,260
I don’t want to be an emperor

400
00:19:12,260 --> 00:19:14,360
who can’t keep his words.

401
00:19:14,860 --> 00:19:16,860
Shall we find an excuse

402
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:17,980
to arrest him?

403
00:19:18,970 --> 00:19:20,130
An excuse?

404
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:23,300
He has been very careful these years.

405
00:19:23,890 --> 00:19:25,820
If I could find an excuse,

406
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:27,490
I would have killed him a long time ago.

407
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:31,260
Then we need a plan

408
00:19:31,540 --> 00:19:33,110
to make everyone think

409
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:35,120
Your Majesty have forgiven him

410
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:36,550
and will let him go back to Yanbei.

411
00:19:36,930 --> 00:19:37,720
Then,

412
00:19:40,020 --> 00:19:42,540
we’ll find a way to get rid of him.

413
00:19:46,260 --> 00:19:47,450
A plan?

414
00:19:59,420 --> 00:20:01,570
Your Majesty,
Princess Chun asked to see you.

415
00:20:02,190 --> 00:20:03,180
Don’t you see

416
00:20:03,180 --> 00:20:04,790
we’re in the middle of something?

417
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:06,030
Tell her to leave.

418
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:07,040
Her Highness insisted

419
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:09,070
she should see you today.

420
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:09,890
Otherwise,

421
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:11,840
she would keep kneeling outside the door.

422
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:15,660
What does she want?

423
00:20:16,180 --> 00:20:17,290
Bring her in.

424
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:18,690
Aye.

425
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:23,760
I shall excuse myself.

426
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:24,730
There is no need.

427
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:26,690
I still have something

428
00:20:26,690 --> 00:20:27,830
to discuss with you.

429
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:29,750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

430
00:20:46,270 --> 00:20:47,920
Greeting, Father.

431
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,150
What do you come for?

432
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:56,610
Father, I don’t want

433
00:20:56,610 --> 00:20:57,990
to marry the Crown Prince of Liang.

434
00:20:58,540 --> 00:21:00,410
Who told you that?

435
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:02,870
Don’t be childish. Go back now.

436
00:21:04,050 --> 00:21:05,050
Father.

437
00:21:05,260 --> 00:21:06,250
If you never

438
00:21:06,250 --> 00:21:07,260
had such a plan,

439
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:09,670
I would say thank you.

440
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,350
However,

441
00:21:11,350 --> 00:21:13,020
if you do,

442
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:15,070
I’m telling you

443
00:21:16,010 --> 00:21:17,210
I will never marry

444
00:21:17,210 --> 00:21:18,770
the Crown Prince of Liang!

445
00:21:18,930 --> 00:21:20,130
I won’t marry him

446
00:21:20,130 --> 00:21:21,180
or anyone else!

447
00:21:21,180 --> 00:21:22,460
I will

448
00:21:22,870 --> 00:21:24,730
marry no one,

449
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:26,510
but Yan Xun!

450
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,150
Your Excellency,

451
00:21:57,140 --> 00:21:58,840
we will leave here soon.

452
00:22:00,060 --> 00:22:02,290
Recently, guards for us

453
00:22:02,290 --> 00:22:03,350
have changed.

454
00:22:03,850 --> 00:22:05,000
They are no longer those

455
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:05,710
who work for Prince Yuan Song.

456
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,330
The Emperor is going to kill me.

457
00:22:17,130 --> 00:22:18,670
He is a hypocritical man

458
00:22:18,670 --> 00:22:19,800
who values fame and wealth.

459
00:22:20,650 --> 00:22:22,430
Envoys of Liang are still here.

460
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:24,150
In recent years,

461
00:22:24,360 --> 00:22:25,970
we’ve spread the news to everyone

462
00:22:26,130 --> 00:22:27,700
that you were spared

463
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:29,320
and will go back to Yanbei.

464
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:33,050
Even if the Emperor wants to kill you,

465
00:22:33,670 --> 00:22:35,470
he doesn’t dare to do it in the public.

466
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,650
Looks like we are about to have the chance

467
00:22:37,650 --> 00:22:38,510
to leave Chang’an.

468
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:44,720
So, be careful with food

469
00:22:45,050 --> 00:22:46,220
and watch out for assassinators lately

470
00:22:48,030 --> 00:22:49,910
in case the Emperor
takes desperate action.

471
00:22:53,100 --> 00:22:54,450
But I think

472
00:22:54,770 --> 00:22:55,990
the Emperor

473
00:22:55,990 --> 00:22:57,500
will probably

474
00:22:57,500 --> 00:22:58,790
show kindness to you

475
00:22:58,790 --> 00:23:00,000
in order

476
00:23:00,530 --> 00:23:02,060
to convince people

477
00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:03,010
that he has kept his promise

478
00:23:03,010 --> 00:23:04,200
and will let you live.

479
00:23:04,200 --> 00:23:05,650
Then he will kill you by surprise

480
00:23:05,770 --> 00:23:07,240
so that he can get away with it.

481
00:23:07,810 --> 00:23:09,160
Show kindness to me?

482
00:23:10,850 --> 00:23:11,600
The only way he can show the world

483
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:13,760
that he has kept his words

484
00:23:13,950 --> 00:23:15,770
would be letting me go back to Yanbei.

485
00:23:17,010 --> 00:23:18,820
Yet this is exactly the last thing
he would do.

486
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:21,480
Your Excellency.

487
00:23:25,170 --> 00:23:27,430
Your Excellency,
someone came from the Palace,

488
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:29,450
saying His Majesty wanted to see you.

489
00:23:39,400 --> 00:23:41,740
Greetings, Your Majesty.

490
00:23:42,870 --> 00:23:45,600
Long live Your Majesty.

491
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:49,120
You may rise.

492
00:23:49,820 --> 00:23:50,910
Thank you, Your Majesty.

493
00:23:56,570 --> 00:23:59,500
Yan Xun, how are you doing lately?

494
00:24:00,730 --> 00:24:03,310
Thanks to you, Your Majesty,
everything is fine.

495
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:06,030
You have focused on studying these years

496
00:24:06,030 --> 00:24:07,660
and barely gone out.

497
00:24:08,060 --> 00:24:11,200
You have become calmer.

498
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:12,660
Good.

499
00:24:12,660 --> 00:24:14,770
You are going to govern a land

500
00:24:14,770 --> 00:24:16,370
for me.

501
00:24:17,960 --> 00:24:19,440
A general like you

502
00:24:19,990 --> 00:24:21,960
should be calm.

503
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,310
Thank you, Your Majesty.

504
00:24:25,810 --> 00:24:27,090
This year,

505
00:24:28,320 --> 00:24:30,880
you’re twenty-two, aren’t you?

506
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:32,380
I’m twenty-three.

507
00:24:34,680 --> 00:24:36,600
It’s an age to get married then.

508
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:38,330
Do you have anyone in mind?

509
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,130
No.

510
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:42,920
Before having achieved anything,

511
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:44,660
I don’t dare to get married.

512
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:49,080
People make up a family before work.

513
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:51,460
They usually get married first.

514
00:24:52,070 --> 00:24:53,660
Your parents are gone.

515
00:24:53,660 --> 00:24:55,180
I ought to take care of you.

516
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:57,020
Even if you don’t want to get married,

517
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,460
I still need to handle that.

518
00:24:59,010 --> 00:25:00,950
Your Majesty, I…

519
00:25:01,470 --> 00:25:02,190
Right.

520
00:25:02,700 --> 00:25:06,100
I have someone suitable for you.

521
00:25:07,410 --> 00:25:08,730
You and my daughter

522
00:25:08,730 --> 00:25:11,050
grew up together.

523
00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:13,210
You make a perfect couple.

524
00:25:15,070 --> 00:25:17,420
She has a bad temper.

525
00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:18,140
But she is kind

526
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:20,470
and polite.

527
00:25:20,470 --> 00:25:21,970
I would be worried

528
00:25:21,970 --> 00:25:23,480
if she married anyone else.

529
00:25:23,630 --> 00:25:24,540
I watched it

530
00:25:24,540 --> 00:25:26,480
when you grew up.

531
00:25:28,150 --> 00:25:29,700
I can’t be relieved

532
00:25:29,700 --> 00:25:31,370
unless I marry her to you.

533
00:25:39,310 --> 00:25:42,660
Your Majesty, I am the son of a traitor.

534
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:44,750
It is your mercy

535
00:25:44,750 --> 00:25:45,820
to let me live.

536
00:25:46,190 --> 00:25:47,930
How can I expect to marry Her Highness?

537
00:25:48,370 --> 00:25:50,430
Your Majesty, please take it back.

538
00:25:51,050 --> 00:25:52,260
You don’t want that?

539
00:25:53,610 --> 00:25:55,170
I’m not good enough for Her Highness.

540
00:25:56,470 --> 00:25:57,810
I hear

541
00:25:57,990 --> 00:25:59,590
you are

542
00:25:59,590 --> 00:26:02,100
very close to your maid,

543
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:04,090
Chu Qiao.

544
00:26:04,580 --> 00:26:06,670
Are you refusing to marry my daughter

545
00:26:07,230 --> 00:26:09,180
because of her?

546
00:26:09,870 --> 00:26:11,420
She not only

547
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:13,620
bewitches the Crown Prince of Liang

548
00:26:14,220 --> 00:26:16,420
but also steals my future son-in-law.

549
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:18,000
How dare she!

550
00:26:32,620 --> 00:26:33,980
Concubine Lan wanted to see me?

551
00:26:36,300 --> 00:26:37,650
That’s right, Ms. Chu.

552
00:26:37,650 --> 00:26:39,450
Please come to the Palace with me.

553
00:26:39,450 --> 00:26:41,230
Her Grace is waiting for you.

554
00:26:42,140 --> 00:26:42,800
Okay.

555
00:26:43,030 --> 00:26:43,700
Please.

556
00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:51,930
Your Majesty, that’s not true.

557
00:26:52,810 --> 00:26:54,910
When my father committed the crime

558
00:26:55,060 --> 00:26:56,150
and got my families killed,

559
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:58,550
I lost everything overnight.

560
00:26:58,720 --> 00:27:00,190
It is because of your mercy

561
00:27:00,190 --> 00:27:01,670
that I survived.

562
00:27:02,220 --> 00:27:03,540
Over the past three years,

563
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,780
I have felt ashamed of

564
00:27:04,780 --> 00:27:05,960
what my father did

565
00:27:06,430 --> 00:27:08,140
and I have been depressed.

566
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:09,250
But she

567
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:11,280
kept me company

568
00:27:11,710 --> 00:27:13,280
and encouraged me to cheer up.

569
00:27:13,910 --> 00:27:15,280
To me,

570
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,770
she is not just a maid,

571
00:27:17,080 --> 00:27:18,400
but more like a family.

572
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:20,020
Yet we don’t love

573
00:27:21,370 --> 00:27:22,530
each other.

574
00:27:28,250 --> 00:27:29,460
Father.

575
00:27:30,030 --> 00:27:32,090
Your assumption is not true.

576
00:27:32,090 --> 00:27:33,580
Don’t imagine things.

577
00:27:33,580 --> 00:27:34,890
