00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:40,860
You sound so reasonable

869
00:39:40,860 --> 00:39:42,390
these days!

870
00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:52,020
= Weipin Pavilion =

871
00:39:53,790 --> 00:39:54,800
He is gone.

872
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:56,670
Won’t you give her the present?

873
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,820
Seems like he isn’t too stupid.

874
00:40:01,570 --> 00:40:02,510
He has straightened his thinking.

875
00:40:02,510 --> 00:40:03,460
Why would he love

876
00:40:03,460 --> 00:40:04,690
someone like you?

877
00:40:06,010 --> 00:40:07,400
Just be jealous.

878
00:40:07,890 --> 00:40:09,290
I’m not jealous at all.

879
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:17,740
What? They’ll get married.

880
00:40:17,980 --> 00:40:20,210
Yes, it will be announced soon.

881
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:21,880
But time is running out.

882
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,050
Ministers of Rites

883
00:40:23,050 --> 00:40:24,650
have started to prepare for the wedding.

884
00:40:24,650 --> 00:40:25,750
How could His Majesty

885
00:40:25,750 --> 00:40:26,790
marry Her Highness to Yan Xun?

886
00:40:27,140 --> 00:40:27,800
He killed

887
00:40:27,800 --> 00:40:29,270
Yan Xun’s whole family.

888
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:30,490
Yan Xun also saw his mother

889
00:40:30,490 --> 00:40:31,610
kill herself

890
00:40:31,610 --> 00:40:32,540
on Jiuyou Platform.

891
00:40:33,010 --> 00:40:34,300
How can a wedding

892
00:40:34,300 --> 00:40:35,290
relieve him

893
00:40:35,290 --> 00:40:36,470
from such hatred?

894
00:40:38,240 --> 00:40:40,010
If Her Highness marries Yan Xun,

895
00:40:40,010 --> 00:40:41,560
she’ll never be happy!

896
00:40:42,130 --> 00:40:43,330
Young Master Wei.

897
00:40:43,660 --> 00:40:45,680
No, he can’t agree.

898
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:46,740
I’ll go see His Majesty.

899
00:40:46,740 --> 00:40:47,730
He can’t do that.

900
00:40:47,730 --> 00:40:48,590
Young Master Wei.

901
00:40:48,590 --> 00:40:49,890
- Don’t be impulsive.
- Let go of me!

902
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:50,790
Do you want Her Highness

903
00:40:50,790 --> 00:40:52,010
to hate you all her whole life?

904
00:40:53,210 --> 00:40:54,840
I am just a little maid

905
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:56,000
who knows nothing.

906
00:40:56,190 --> 00:40:56,840
But I have served Her Highness

907
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,160
since I was little.

908
00:40:58,160 --> 00:40:59,170
I know

909
00:40:59,170 --> 00:41:00,240
she always likes

910
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:01,180
His Excellency Yan Xun.

911
00:41:01,490 --> 00:41:02,720
She wants to marry him.

912
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:04,380
That is her biggest dream.

913
00:41:05,550 --> 00:41:07,250
Now her dream will

914
00:41:07,250 --> 00:41:08,740
come true.

915
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:10,280
Young Master Wei.

916
00:41:10,810 --> 00:41:11,490
Are you going

917
00:41:11,490 --> 00:41:13,500
to break her dream?

918
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,550
But...

919
00:41:17,470 --> 00:41:19,180
Yan Xun doesn’t like her!

920
00:41:19,180 --> 00:41:20,780
Why are you so sure?

921
00:41:21,380 --> 00:41:22,820
Even if that’s true,

922
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:24,650
she will still marry him.

923
00:41:25,290 --> 00:41:27,220
No. No way!

924
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:29,040
Even if she hates me,

925
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:30,070
hits me, curses me,

926
00:41:30,070 --> 00:41:31,030
or blames me,

927
00:41:31,450 --> 00:41:32,810
I cannot see her

928
00:41:32,810 --> 00:41:33,890
jumping into fire!

929
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,680
I must stop her!

930
00:41:36,450 --> 00:41:37,850
Can you?

931
00:41:38,960 --> 00:41:39,830
Young Master Wei.

932
00:41:40,230 --> 00:41:41,900
Minister Wei Guang has passed away.

933
00:41:42,070 --> 00:41:43,860
Your family is no longer as powerful.

934
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:46,600
Even Her Grace fails

935
00:41:46,600 --> 00:41:47,820
to stop that,

936
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:50,190
do you think

937
00:41:50,190 --> 00:41:51,220
you can stop them?

938
00:41:52,490 --> 00:41:53,530
Young Master Wei.

939
00:41:53,990 --> 00:41:55,870
I know you are nice to Her Highness.

940
00:41:56,150 --> 00:41:57,230
But I also want you

941
00:41:57,230 --> 00:41:58,310
to be nice to yourself.

942
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:01,320
If you really stop her,

943
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:03,020
I’m afraid

944
00:42:03,020 --> 00:42:04,410
Her Highness will never

945
00:42:04,410 --> 00:42:05,530
talk to you again.

946
00:42:06,450 --> 00:42:07,800
It doesn’t matter.

947
00:42:09,230 --> 00:42:10,860
Even if she never talks to me again,

948
00:42:11,750 --> 00:42:12,820
it doesn’t matter.

949
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:16,270
I just want her

950
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:17,670
to be happy

951
00:42:18,130 --> 00:42:19,530
and live a good life.

952
00:42:20,940 --> 00:42:22,280
Even if I die for her,

953
00:42:23,810 --> 00:42:25,090
I will feel relieved.

954
00:42:27,310 --> 00:42:30,330
Young Master Wei, Her Highness understands

955
00:42:30,630 --> 00:42:32,140
what you just said

956
00:42:32,640 --> 00:42:34,320
and what you worry about.

957
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,210
But she still wants

958
00:42:37,210 --> 00:42:37,940
to have a try.

959
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:40,210
She has loved him for so many years.

960
00:42:40,210 --> 00:42:41,710
She can’t just let it go.

961
00:42:43,160 --> 00:42:44,360
What if His Excellency Yan Xun

962
00:42:44,360 --> 00:42:45,330
could let go of all hatred

963
00:42:45,330 --> 00:42:46,370
and accept her?

964
00:43:36,970 --> 00:43:38,150
You want to see me when it’s so late.

965
00:43:38,150 --> 00:43:39,420
What happened?

966
00:43:39,420 --> 00:43:40,870
I just want to see you.

967
00:43:43,140 --> 00:43:43,920
Achu.

968
00:43:44,800 --> 00:43:46,430
About the wedding
between Her Highness and me...

969
00:43:46,430 --> 00:43:47,290
I know.

